GAZETTE, 24 JULY, 1947

The Commander-in-Chief, Mediterranean. Forwarded, concurring with Commanding Officer, H.M.S. ILLUSTRIOUS report. From information at present available this attack has achieved considerable success, Recommendations under Mediterranean Con- fidential Memorandum 115 are being forwarded separately.
